    {
      "id": "b55fd517-c399-4180-8593-174017c3900b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper focuses on Deep Learning to develop recommender systems of new content. The paper introduces a new model to detect students at risk using GRU. Model was assessed on dataset featuring 16000 records of student assessments from various institutions.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "b55fd517-c399-4180-8593-174017c3900b",
