    {
      "id": "f7e4be25-c9e7-4bf2-9b64-6bb9408b0f0d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The system was compared against other deep learning based recomender systems. Its unclear to me what is being recommmended though. High accuracy of the model signals the importance of these models in addressing underachievement and potential dropout.",
